miinimumnouded:
Positiivse tulemuse saamiseks peab:
1) osalema vähemalt 80% Zoomi tundides (lubatud on 3 puudumist);
2) sooritama 3 testi (vähemalt 51% õigeid vastuseid igas testis);
3) sooritama harjutused Moodle'is. Harjutuste eest on võimalik saada 20 punkti kokku. Iga tegemata või sooritamata harjutuse eest saab ühe miinuspunkti. Kui sooritamata on rohkem kui 25 harjutust, siis harjutuste eest punkte ei saa. Kui rohkem kui 50 harjutust on sooritamata, siis üliõpilane ei soorita kursust. Kõikidel harjutustel on tähtajad, palun tähtaegadest kinni pidada. NB! Pärast tähtaja möödumist ei avata Moodle'i harjutusi uuesti, iga tegemata harjutuse eest saab miinuspunkti.
4) sooritama suulise eksami.

In order to get a positive result one must
1) attend actively at least 80% of the Zoom-sessions (it is allowed to miss 3 times);
2) pass 3 Moodle tests (at least 51% must be correct); 
3) submit the Moodle exercises. It is possible to get 20 points for all the Moodle exercises. One minus point for every uncompleted exercises (less than 50% of the answers are correct), if there are more than 25 exercises uncompleted, then one will not get points for exercises. If more than 50 exercises are not completed before the deadline (less than 50% of the answers are correct) then the student can not pass this course. All the exercises have deadlines, please make sure you submit the exercises on time. NB! After the deadline has passed, the Moodle exercises will not be opened again, each unsubmitted exercise will give one minus point.
4) passing an oral exam.

NB! A student who hasn't missed any Zoom-sessions and has been active in all of the Zoom-sessions does not need to take the oral exam.

Being active in the Zoom-session means that
a) the web-camera is turned on;
b) the student is speaking and interacting with the teacher and other students during the Zoom-session;
c) the student is present during the whole Zoom-session.

